  "title": "chore(docs): switch to jekyll 3, digest all assets",
  "body": "It was a bit of a nightmare: I only wanted to digest all assets and thought it would be easy.\n\nTurns ou I had to move to jekyll 3, then handle a lot of weird sh## (expected).\n\nIn the end, everything is working but I was unable to make the dev docs task mount the website on the virtual /instantsearch.js/ path.\n\nI guess it was working before, but it's no more. Submitted some issues to relevant (I hope) projects.\n\nIn the meantime, this should be merged\n- digest all assets to avoid caching issues\n- concatenate scripts that can be contenated\n- minify css and js\n",
